func_of_funk <- function(x, k = 1) {
  if (k ==1) {
    a <- x %>%  mutate_if(is.character, as.factor) %>% select_if(is.factor) %>% select_if(~length(levels(.)) < 4)
    a1 <- names(a)
    a2 <- seq_along(a1)
    
    map(a2, function(p) {
      map(a2[-p], function(t) {
            ggplot(a) + geom_bar(aes_string(a1[p], fill=a1[t]))
            })
        })
  } else if (k ==2) {
    a <- x %>% select_if(is.numeric)
    a1 <- names(a)
    a2 <- seq_along(a1)
    
    map(a2, function(p) {
      ggplot(a) + geom_density(aes_string(a1[p]))
    })
    
  } else if (k==3) {
    a <- x %>%  mutate_if(is.character, as.factor) %>% select_if(is.factor) %>% select_if(~length(levels(.)) < 4)
    a1 <- names(a)
    a2 <- seq_along(a1)
    
    b <- x %>% select_if(is.numeric)
    b1 <- names(b)
    b2 <- seq_along(b1)
    
    c<-cbind(a,b)
    
    map(b2, function(p){
      map(a2, function(t){
        ggplot(c,aes_string(x=b1[p], col=a1[t])) + geom_density()
      })
    })
  }
  
}
func_of_funk(titanic, k=3)

linear_Model_R <- function(x) {
  a <- x %>% select_if(is.numeric)
  a1 <- seq_along(names(a))
  b <- data.frame(matrix(ncol=3,nrow=0))
  colnames(b) <- c("x1", "x2", "R_Square")
  i=1
  map(a1, function(p) {
    map(a1[-p], function(t){
      c <- 0
      c <- summary(lm(a[[p]]~a[[t]], a))$r.square
      options(scipen = 999)
      d <- as.data.frame(matrix(c(names(a[p]), names(a[t])), nrow = 1, ncol=2))
      e <- cbind(d,c)
      colnames(e) <- c("x1", "x2", "R_Square")
      
      b <<- rbind(b,e)
      
      
    })
    
  })
  print(b)
}

linear_Model_R(titanic)
